interpretation: The garlic emoji represents protection, strength, and healing. Garlic has been used for centuries to ward off evil spirits and protect against sickness and disease. This card may indicate the need for increased protection or the presence of negative energy in your life. It can also suggest the need for physical strength and stamina to overcome challenges. Garlic is also associated with healing and may indicate a need for self-care and taking care of one's health. This card may encourage you to focus on cleansing and purifying your mind, body, and spirit.
